{"tid":289422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［多圖］大波 啡lin 多p","createTime":"2017-06-19T03:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T07:46:48.000Z","uid":81507,"like":197,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5295aba33791bc787ac26e1c01da2a1d838cbb20","tid":289422,"uid":81507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T03:56:55.000Z","msg":"話說有晚好無野做，約左個fd去體育館篤下波波<br />\n<br />\n一上到去有兩張波檯，一張有一男一女玩緊，另一張就有成班細路<br />\n我地張飛就係成班細路個張檯<br />\n<br />\n好喇，夠鐘交檯喇，我地見到張咁既檯<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/112536_6d5eb966825cf1509a450c78c00fa5c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F112536_6d5eb966825cf1509a450c78c00fa5c3.jpg&h=7468585b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我同個fd呆左呆，不過都心諗，話唔定唔係佢地做既呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後就開始玩，無諗咁多<br />\n點知玩左差唔多一個鐘頭，佢地又返返黎，原來佢地book左隔離張檯再玩過<br />\n<br />\n跟住就過癮喇<br />\n<br />\n個桌球室唔知做乜，仲凍過殮房<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我同個fd都只係著左件tee，凍都手指都痺埋<br />\n點知班人入面有個大隻仔見佢女朋友（唔知係咪）好凍，當場除左件衫比佢褸住，自己就赤膊篤波<br />\n除左佩服都唔知講咩好<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/113623_17e10c6c4ded33a11d05f65523b4bdc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F113623_17e10c6c4ded33a11d05f65523b4bdc3.jpg&h=4c3bfd43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一個大隻仔有樣學樣，show晒d胸肌腹肌出黎<br />\n見佢地咁fit，忍唔住影多左兩張<br />\n［img]<a href=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/114034_f6198db6b79736c8fb561c1cf4180306.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F114034_f6198db6b79736c8fb561c1cf4180306.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=zGjnhggtEuWaQdY2yEmPV4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=cec2a7de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/114034_f6198db6b79736c8fb561c1cf4180306.jpg[/img]</a><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/114036_6732dfd1ae59771c9cac619fddf19272.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F114036_6732dfd1ae59771c9cac619fddf19272.jpg&h=d6aa156e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住有條女揸住支Q爬左上張波檯，遠睇有少少似比緊武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/114430_630f8562db9ecc1fc0646152d1b100ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F114430_630f8562db9ecc1fc0646152d1b100ff.jpg&h=39b0f65e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/114432_2f00b9665a3eb681cbae97af3f2c8b85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F114432_2f00b9665a3eb681cbae97af3f2c8b85.jpg&h=6d9de2f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/114434_cc5833ea8994b2af9733ffc89bb74954.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F114434_cc5833ea8994b2af9733ffc89bb74954.jpg&h=5030a3fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪峨眉派既劍法<br />\n你知啦，我黎篤波架咋，真係無咩研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n［img]<a href=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/114435_758aabbbf5bec49a3c86ebabb1656067.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F114435_758aabbbf5bec49a3c86ebabb1656067.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=zGjnhggtEuWaQdY2yEmPV4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=5c4ddf09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/114435_758aabbbf5bec49a3c86ebabb1656067.jpg[/img]</a><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/114438_ae47bae82fce45aea6f7425d46b4a5cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F114438_ae47bae82fce45aea6f7425d46b4a5cb.jpg&h=e976121e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDoggy Doggy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/114928_a19782e41f7f85a9a9303be9e665f01f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F114928_a19782e41f7f85a9a9303be9e665f01f.jpg&h=4c5709c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連hehe既都有，又係既，得兩條女，點夠分<br />\n不過小弟有潔癖，要我除衫係地下碌，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/115150_12123d1357a9436e99ac1845c3aef5d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F115150_12123d1357a9436e99ac1845c3aef5d0.jpg&h=70caaec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家d細路真係幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 年紀細細咁識玩<br />\n大家千奇唔好推，由得個post石沉大海算啦<br />\n呢d年頭公德心唔值錢架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb303d6f75795237301b90206a62f4071f3ea50","tid":289422,"uid":118551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T03:57:48.000Z","msg":"桌球天王"},{"pid":"a17fbc8078f9069f9598a63e3793fc4395d1694b","tid":289422,"uid":21837,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T03:58:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d6764befb37f95584cc002f6ad18940460ed0f","tid":289422,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T03:59:14.000Z","msg":"啡lin 唔算睇到 大波呢"},{"pid":"8a785b7760541cbc53126c023e1320c60312a3e2","tid":289422,"uid":81507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T03:59:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啡lin 唔算睇到 大波呢</blockquote><br />\n大過好多港女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gi